(1, 1, 'Ice cream', 'ice-cream', 'Ice cream is a sweetened frozen food typically eaten as a snack or dessert. It is usually made from dairy products, such as milk and cream, and often combined with fruits or other ingredients and flavors. It is typically sweetened with sugar or sugar substitutes.', 0, 'icecream.jpg', 1, 1, 1, '2016-10-27 11:21:36', '2018-03-19 00:18:16', 1, 1),
(10, 3, 'Onion Ring', 'onion_ring', 'Highly delicious and addictive. Our raw onion rings are delightfully spicy and sweet composition of raw onions covered by fresh dried fruits, species, fresh turmeric and ginger root, garlic, Indian seasoning and sunflower seeds. Eat them by themselves, they are also highly nutritious or have the along your salad or any product you need extra', 105, 'onionring.jpg', 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 0),
