(50, 8, 'Handcrafted Owl Coaster', 'handcrafted-owl-coaster', 'Set of 4 cork- bottomed drinks costars with rounded corners. Durable, high quality and easy to maintain. These are perfect for home entertainment, celebrations and parties.', 360, 'b1d8a078626d77ed08dd20311a553250.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:48:31', '2018-08-23 18:48:31', 1, 0),
(51, 8, 'Embossed Hand Painted Wooden Blue Parrot Jar Set', 'embossed-hand-painted-wooden-blue-parrot-jar-set', 'Hand Crafted By National Award Winner Artist Abshar Husain.Bring this coloured parrot Jar set from our \"BIRD COLLECTION\" in multicolour to elevate the beauty of your dining setup and add an elegance to your kitchen accessory collection.Bring this blue coloured parrot Jar set from our \"BIRD COLLECTION\" in blue colour with emboss coloured handpainting to elevate the beauty of your dinning setup and add an elegancy to your kitchen accessory collection. The beauty of this jar set has handcrafted wooden parrots sitting on top of each jar and on the top of the holder. This refereshener jar set with a tray holder is used to store refresheners, Spices and knick knacks and comes with a spoon. The tray is used to hold all the 4 unique set of parrot jars which has an exquisite way to carry it from the top and a parrot is placed on the top of the holder. ART TYPE: Tota Collection. NOTE: 1) Comes with a) 4 Jars & lids b) 4 spoons c) 1 Tray 2) Wood may have marks/patches which are natural. 3)', 1349, 'fc04e71079ad0980e362421f33ff0bf9.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:50:56', '2018-08-23 18:50:56', 0, 0),
(52, 8, 'Coasters Lemons and Melons series', 'coasters-lemons-and-melons-series', 'Add style to your home with our wacky coasters, designs have been exclusively illustrated for the summer.', 500, '2b7fa08c0a091d74a2f4477f47cf16ba.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:52:25', '2018-08-23 18:52:25', 0, 0),
(53, 8, 'Handcrafted Round Planters', 'handcrafted-round-planters', 'Welcome some greenery indoors and add a touch of class to your home decor or gift it to someone. The planter does not come with any plants in them.', 325, 'd65c1d3a58c7d454bd219d7729333af9.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:54:13', '2018-08-23 18:54:13', 0, 0),
(54, 8, 'The Floating Grasslands Terrarium DIY Kit', 'the-floating-grasslands-terrarium-diy-kit', 'An urban green solution that is a lush terrarium with giraffes and gives an absolute grassland feel to your home! Use your artistic skills to turn this DIY Kit into the terrarium you dreamt of! Make it a centre of attraction in your home and watch your guests go green with envy. Living in urban flats is no long an excuse. Go Green.', 1800, '15349748c5f96d89b52ea2803bf4e0ce.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:56:11', '2018-08-23 18:56:11', 0, 0),
(55, 8, 'Handcrafted Kauna Reed Tissue Box', 'handcrafted-kauna-reed-tissue-box', 'The Tissue Box from Ziveli is certainly a necessary essential for your home or car. Handcrafted by women artisans from Manipur, this trendy, elegant and earthy box comes with a beautiful lock.', 80, '3288b5754ed5320e8e0983e4a18085d5.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:58:28', '2018-08-23 18:58:28', 0, 0),
(56, 8, 'Wooden Panel with Metal Chandelier', 'wooden-panel-with-metal-chandelier', 'Add charm to your room or garden décor. These hanging lights emanate a glow that is refreshing and captivating. The wooden panel accords an ethnic look. Decorations galore. Note: Height of wires are adjustable.', 5300, '481070c0921afc92497b92c302345af1.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:00:03', '2018-08-23 19:00:03', 0, 0),
(57, 8, 'Green Wooden Small Oval Royal Hand Mirror', 'green-wooden-small-oval-royal-hand-mirror', 'This regal hand carved, a handheld mirror is from the ‘Royal Collection’. Handpainted using natural colours, this piece is ideal to carry around in your purse or simply place it as a decorative in your dressing room.', 550, '70272b53fa0acad44b24e4640b967683.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:01:52', '2018-08-23 19:01:52', 0, 0),
(58, 9, 'Handwoven Khadi Pouch (Light Green)', 'handwoven-khadi-pouch-light-green', 'Khadi is a woven journey into the soul of India. Khadi started a symbol of freedom. Today it represents an evolving India.It brings employment to millions of India craftsmen. Khadi represents a sustainable and spiritual way of life. We bring the best of Khadi with impeccable workmanship to create contemporary Accessories. Celebrate India every day with handcrafted Khadi accessories from Clean Planet, The Khadi pouch is a smart way to carry your essentials in eco style.', 400, '8e1a51dae12d619e7c5cc593c3dd3aef.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:06:43', '2018-08-23 19:06:43', 1, 0),
(59, 9, 'Handcrafted Cork Leather Wallet', 'handcrafted-cork-leather-wallet', 'Handcrafted Cork Leather Wallet is made of cork skin. This wallet has signature detailing with dedicated pockets for your cards, cash and other small essentials Fits in 6 cards along with an external zipped enclosure for keeping coins. This product is dirt and water resistant.', 1500, '2809866c9f8060028e558d11d5fc4366.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:07:56', '2018-08-23 19:07:56', 0, 0),
(60, 9, 'Silver Hair Chain (Matha Patti | Tikka | Wedding Hair Accessory)', 'silver-hair-chain-matha-patti-tikka-wedding-hair-accessory', 'This simple headchain in silver and kundan is a classic piece of head jewelry for a minimalist. The combination of the Kundan tikka with layers in silver chain makes it a must have in your wardrobe. Its lightweight and easy to wear and can be worn by young girls or children too.  Perfect wedding or an engagement gift.', 500, '67f364a5e6ceff48409d881441582dba.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:09:34', '2018-08-23 19:09:34', 0, 0),
(61, 9, 'Multicolor Hair Accessory (Boho | Tassels | Flower | Hair Jewellery | Gold Hair Clip)', 'multicolor-hair-accessory-boho-tassels-flower-hair-jewellery-gold-hair-clip', 'A very smart pair of hair accessories made with multicolored tassels and antique gold metallic charms. The beautiful pattern on the sunflower as engraved contrasts beautifully with the multitude of colors on the tassel. Can be paired with the simplest of outfits to add spunk to the look.  These are very light weight,easy to wear and make for a great gift for your loved one.', 420, 'a696c151aa0cadf3183eff5a2096a779.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:10:52', '2018-08-23 19:10:52', 0, 0),
(62, 9, 'Vintage Indian Potli (Set of 2) (Rust & Gold)', 'vintage-indian-potli-set-of-2-rust-gold', 'Vintage Indian Potli impeccably crafted. Great for carrying essentials or gifting. Joy guaranteed. This product supports livelihood program for women. Earn good karma while looking good.', 400, 'bb1db8d42cbbf0cf1d26423df94a274d.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:12:22', '2018-08-23 19:12:22', 0, 0),
(63, 10, 'Red Velvet Brownies (Pack of 4)', 'red-velvet-brownies-pack-of-4', 'A gift box filled with 4 Red Velvet Brownies.', 360, '6a5856cace2377a92b207eb2a94e54cb.jpg', 2, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:16:32', '2018-08-24 00:22:57', 1, 0),
(64, 10, 'DIY Hazlenut Brownie', 'diy-hazlenut-brownie', 'Do It Yourself Brownie that is gooey and fills the mouth with richness once baked. Easy to bake by anyone and gives the joy of eating a freshly baked brownie at home.', 650, 'bd4b22296f51649bbd55de61c2931c93.jpeg', 2, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:18:02', '2018-08-23 19:18:02', 0, 0),
(65, 10, 'Homemade Marble Chocolate', 'homemade-marble-chocolate', 'A chocolate of a different kind, Ooty Home-made’s marble chocolate is a favourite recipe that has been mastered over time. Thissinful chocolate melts in your mouth, you are transported into another world… a world made of chocolate dreams.', 230, 'bc8cb9fe729b159cf237dc7479c4bb14.jpg', 2, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:20:16', '2018-08-23 19:20:16', 0, 0),
(66, 10, 'Homemade Assorted Chocolates', 'homemade-assorted-chocolates', 'Can’t decide which chocolate to order? You want a little rum and raisin and a few roasted cashews. Fancy some butterscotch or the plain old fruit and nut? How about some milk chocolate and those delicious marble chocolates? Or perhaps, some bitter chocolate with the roasted almond ones? That’s right, with our assorted mix, you can enjoy all our special chocolates in one helluva mix! Did we mentioncrispy chocolate too?', 350, '490d572f80f8c0e5d376c5445da8c568.jpg', 2, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:22:09', '2018-08-23 19:22:09', 0, 0),
(67, 8, 'Handcrafted Wooden Kum Kum Container (Set of 3)', 'handcrafted-wooden-kum-kum-container-set-of-3', 'These pretty wooden containers laid on a wooden plate are fit to store any powdery contents like haldi or kumkum. The containers and plates, are handmade and handpainted using organic vegetable dyes.', 715, '84c6e38e26e0096b8734611e38720879.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:24:04', '2018-08-23 19:24:04', 0, 0),
(68, 11, 'Soaps Gift Hamper (Pack of 4 Soaps)', 'soaps-gift-hamper-pack-of-4-soaps', 'All four of our classic-line soaps bundled into one beautiful powder blue hamper with pretty pink lotuses and a kantha work inspired gold running stitch print.\r\n\r\nOrange and gram flour for deep-cleansing for oily or oiled skin.\r\nTurmeric and basil - for an anti-acne relaxing and uplifting experience for normal skin.\r\nVanilla and cinnamon - for creamy, seductive vanilla-cinnamon scrubbiness for normal skin.\r\nPatchouli - herb power from the 60s for sensitive skin.', 450, '4866f5ada1c66c870734ce2a6349d9cc.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:42:06', '2018-08-23 19:45:49', 0, 0),
(69, 11, 'Spa Bucket gift hamper', 'spa-bucket-gift-hamper', 'Relax your mind and soothe your body with this rejuvenating hamper. This spa hamper consists of 5 completely organic ingredients.\r\n\r\nContents:\r\n\r\nExfoliating Scrub\r\nFoot Soak\r\nSoap\r\nFoot Softer\r\nBody Scrub', 900, '669abab22816de0e393a04f97cfb2ee0.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:43:59', '2018-08-23 19:43:59', 0, 0),
(70, 11, 'Red and Silver Kundan Zardozi Indian Rakhi Set (Set of 2)', 'red-and-silver-kundan-zardozi-indian-rakhi-set-set-of-2', 'This elegant set of two Rakhis, Handcrafted with Silk Threads (Resham), Golden wires/threads (Zardozi), Beads, Stones and Kundan Elements, are finished with fine great quality threads, these are a keepsake for lasting memories.  Both the Rakhis are free size and can be tied to both children as well as adults', 250, '8affc5816f2efb8ae430b70eecb7278d.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:45:29', '2018-08-23 19:45:29', 1, 0),
(71, 11, 'Handcrafted Wooden Christmas Decoration Balls (Set of 5)', 'handcrafted-wooden-christmas-decoration-balls-set-of-5', 'These beautiful handcrafted Christmas tree decorations are made of wood. The decorations are coated with natural dyes mixed with lacquer. This set is delivered in a pretty package made of the stem of the banana plant.', 340, 'ed2672e10772d56adf6d51e6b6ce5db8.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:46:56', '2018-08-23 19:46:56', 0, 0),
(72, 11, 'Yellow, Orange and Gold Pearl Bead Rakhi (Handcrafted Lumba Rakhi) (Set of 3)', 'yellow-orange-and-gold-pearl-bead-rakhi-handcrafted-lumba-rakhi-set-of-3', 'A very premium set of Rakhis, in shades of yellow complimented with off white pearls. The bracelet form of Rakhi along with the Lumbas with pearls is augmented by a matched thread Rakhi. Handcrafted with Silk Threads (Resham), Pearls, Golden wires/threads (Zardozi), Beads, Stones and finished with fine great quality threads, these Rakhis are great keepsakes.', 450, '967d2f5df75f1bb842d5d926854ff891.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:48:38', '2018-08-23 19:48:38', 0, 0),
(73, 12, 'Cozy Rattan Chair', 'cozy-rattan-chair', 'In keeping with the funky, \'70s bohemian vibe that\'s been infiltrating home decor lately, wicker (and rattan) furniture is on its way back . But this isn\'t your Grandma\'s wicker; these pieces exude casual cool, simultaneously textured and streamlined. If you\'re looking for a wicker or rattan chair to add a bit of that laid back vibe to your living room, look no further than this..', 4500, '5206029eea1457b7a7489ec1dd0d6ff2.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:59:27', '2018-08-24 00:21:29', 1, 0),
(74, 12, 'Diamond Rattan Chair', 'diamond-rattan-chair', 'A bold style handmade chair that really takes advantage of the unique qualities of the medium.', 3500, '3b587a834283cb369d2f0da32999f2de.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 20:01:21', '2018-08-23 20:01:21', 0, 0),
(75, 12, 'Stone Shape Chair', 'stone-shape-chair', 'For an outdoor  fun and enjoyment of nature with a cup of coffee do not miss this.', 2500, '92e628a946068f0623392d198634a2c0.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 20:03:11', '2018-08-23 20:03:11', 0, 0),
(76, 12, 'Rocking Chair', 'rocking-chair', 'For reading book and newspaper in outdoor environment try to not miss this hand made Rocking Chair.', 5800, '05789fc024a5fcbbcf674a626d41df35.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '2018-08-23 20:05:56', '2018-08-23 20:05:56', 0, 0);

