(7, 'Women Clothes', 'Women-Clothes', 'Designers in over twenty countries create and market bespoke accessories woven by the delicate, skilled hands of over 100 women in Central India. Their products are unique. Many yarns are handspun from organic cottons, dyed with 100% natural dyes and loomed with the utmost care and attention.', 'c3f87ba3bcae695cb3d86797bade39f3.jpg', 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:04:01', '2018-08-24 00:17:31'),
(8, 'Home Decor', 'Home-Decor', 'If you’ve an undeniable passion for interior decorations, our curated collection of naturally produced and handcrafted home décor is sure to please. Order online from a variety of home decor products to spruce up your home in style – from the living room to your kitchen and dining and even your garden & outdoor space. If your home is frequented by guests – buy from our coasters, serving trays, table mats and cushion covers, hand-designed to look like works of art. Or if you love highlighting your space with interesting add-ons, purchase from our quirky, classy and handcrafted – decorative skulls, unique wall décor, clocks, bottle art and even artifacts. Order now from Qtrove a splendid home decor range to give your house the perfect makeover!', '1760909ac3de1cadf819522c2f6a70e7.jpg', 1, 0, '2018-08-23 18:46:28', '2018-08-23 20:18:54'),
(9, 'Fashion', 'Fashion', 'Men and Women', 'fa6f5204ee78f4ffd0753603dc24e8d7.jpg', 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:05:38', '2018-08-23 19:05:38'),
(10, 'Snacks', 'Snacks', 'Sweet and slaty', '5989eac805a77c8cad6caa73d0379c64.png', 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:15:22', '2018-08-23 19:15:55'),
(11, 'Gift', 'Gift', 'Festivals are all about family, friends, colleagues and lots of happiness. It is the start of a new year where there is positivity in the air. The aura of gifting each other goodies remains one of the prominent rituals during any festival. It is a joyous moment when your gift brings happiness to your dear ones. However, it is even better when your gifts are handmade from the under privileged, in-turn giving yourself an immeasurable satisfaction from your heart of gifting something as well as helping a needy person.', '0d81a879718d937121e8bfdff05dc792.jpg', 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:40:06', '2018-08-23 20:18:22'),
(12, 'Furniture', 'Furniture', 'Handmade furniture is tangible, sensual, and personal. The carefully crafted piece of furniture is embedded with a personal energy that no piece from Ikea or a department store can ever replicate. The world of interior design is cluttered by poorly made and mass produced reproduction furniture.', '23ec8ccfddbd76535d5077f9ef38dc04.jpg', 1, 0, '2018-08-23 19:51:07', '2018-08-23 20:16:47');

